  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>LEADING THE MARKET SINCE 1969 </strong>- Self-Adhesive Tape Manufacturer &amp; Distributor</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are hiring and looking for resourceful and highly motivated individuals to join our expanding Marketing teams as:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Sales Executive</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>GCE \"O\" / \"N\" Level</li>\n  <li>Possess own car</li>\n  <li>Basic salary + Commission + Transport + Bonus etc</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Identify and pursue new business opportunities and developing strategies to increase sales;</li>\n  <li>Manage and ensure achieving monthly sales target;</li>\n  <li>Ensure consistent and abundant monthly sales in pipelines;</li>\n  <li>Build and maintain excellent relationship with clients and business partners;</li>\n  <li>Research and understand the changing dynamics impacting businesses;</li>\n  <li>Generate creative ideas to capture additional market share.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Own car with minimum 3 years of relevant working experience in packaging industry preferred;</li>\n  <li>Diploma or equivalent qualification in Sales and Marketing an advantage;</li>\n  <li>Ability to identify and pursue new business opportunities and develop strategies to increase sales;</li>\n  <li>Proficient computer skills, including MS Word ad Excel.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
